Cell["\<\
Irreducible representations of the symmetric group are difficult to \
construct. In contrast, it is easy to write down a sufficiently rich family \
of compound representations, whose characters are given here:\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1867315753,ExpressionUUID->"ee144d60-e372-4784-9e4c-8b0c65890800"],

